Title: ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥[ANN][ICO] INVOLVE | JOIN,EARN,BE INVOLVED!ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥
Body: Low commision and no annual fees.  Major mobile app stores are taking 30% of mobile app revenue, while usage of our platform will require only 10%. Within the platform, developers will be free from continuous distraction by marketing processes, while developing apps. Developers will feel free to expose what they are working on and find the vital support and strong feedback, if needed. Besides, there is a great possibility to increase the profits of developers by reducing their costs.  Mobile mining.  ICoin will be the in-platform currency. ICoin can be used for trading among gamers. Every single user will be rewarded once a block is mined according to the time he/she spends playing mobile games or using other apps from out platform. The in-app spending of coins will be registered as developersâ€™ and platformâ€™s revenue, which will eventually pile the strong economic base for the ICoin price.  Voting services.  Our platform is based on the principle stating that everyone has equal rights. Occasionally, we will list number of games able for crowdfunding and gamers will choose which they prefer. Games, which need donation, will be posted at crowdfunding section, where everyone can participate and finance developers using our coins.  Crowdfunding services.  Gaming investors will receive in-game tokens, which they can then sell to users with significant margin. The process of selling of received tokens will be automatic, investors will only need to decide when to process  Share of profits.  The size of reward will depend on the size of the holderâ€™s stake in ITokens.  Exchange  Integrated exchange into platform for convenience of all Involved parties.  For advertisers  Advertisers get a better platform where the audience is more loyal to advertising. This means that the conversion will be higher and, consequently, the cost of attracting one particular client will decrease. The key point is that the ads will be selected in the way they attract users, and advertisers get the best results.

These ten whales can hold a token until the end of the century, but its price will not grow, simply because of the technical absence of any trades on the market.

Body: Hello there,  Coins wont deprecieate because of inside business model we came up with.   The real idea behind us is that we are going to switch the model of monetization of mobile app market. How is that? By creating well working and liquid system of transactions between participants and establishing the united mean of exchange for the market participants. Any transaction, from any participant of the market, no matter what currency is he/she using, has to go through the exchange to our ICoin. Neither more nor less. Consequently, any future miner on our platform will benefit more and more (and, eventually, will find him/herself hodling)  What does that mean? Basically, flow of crypto in the platform will affect the supply and demand (supply decreases due to mining and demand is quite stable --> increase of value of ICoin. Moreover,  it is mentioned in the WP, IToken will represent the right on the share of profit of the platform.  I hope I could answer your question =)
